static-methods&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=ec8f5e67\" target=\"_blank\">http://stackoverflow.com/questions/2671496/java-when-to-use-static-methods</a><br />\n<br />\nOne rule-of-thumb: ask yourself &quot;does it make sense to call this method, even if no Obj has been constructed yet?&quot; If so, it should definitely be static.</blockquote><br />\n都唔係好明 即係幾時先要用"},{"pid":"36e82e5f9cde9cba15d40a3e86a6b234f0ab2eb1","tid":222003,"uid":7099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T09:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64504b8eecd5b1486a637329e4868b6e7eb81e2f","tid":222003,"uid":82301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T09:50:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/questions/2671496/java-when-to-use-static-methods\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstackoverflow.com%2Fquestions%2F2671496%2Fjava-when-to-use-static-methods&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=ec8f5e67\" target=\"_blank\">http://stackoverflow.com/questions/2671496/java-when-to-use-static-methods</a><br />\n<br />\nOne rule-of-thumb: ask yourself &quot;does it make sense to call this method, even if no Obj has been constructed yet?&quot; If so, it should definitely be static.</blockquote><br />\n都唔係好明 即係幾時先要用</blockquote><br />\n如果你整果個係一個Object果時就non static，如果你整嘅係Class就static<br />\n<br />\n我個人會咁樣分：<br />\n如果個class係object class就non static<br />\n如果個class係啲method class(例如啲做converter嘅class，library class果啲)就會用static"},{"pid":"568d45043bdcdc932677d27afc43047dd2e2d0eb","tid":222003,"uid":83015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T09:50:31.000Z","msg":"我用 static會係 喺  variable/ method 係電腦世界 上是 only one, uncountable<br />\n就會用<br />\n<br />\n例如 math.abs , mah既 pi"},{"pid":"78a276223a151eaa36c55989ac00145f92a4385f","tid":222003,"uid":7099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,